data.description: NEW CONSTRUCTION !! Amazing space (3440 square feet) and a great location! Edmond schools and OKC utilities! with 4 bed rooms and 3.5 bath rooms, and 3 car garage there is plenty of space for every one. There are 3 living areas (including an office, family room and bonus/theater room) and a large eating area (and a huge island breakfast bar too!) Kitchen features a farm sink, professional vent hood, gas cook top, oven and microwave. Save up to 50% on heating and cooling costs with a 16 seer A/C, 96% efficient furnace, Navien tankless water heater. Quartz counters throughout. Sprinkler system, security system, pre wired surround sound. Plenty of storage cabinets and linens throw-out the house.
